rows.label: tlk44400287_03_msg0001
rows.name:
The situation we were all so anxious to
avoid seems to be all but inevitable.

rows.label: tlk44400287_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Luxurian science has not evolved in
the way that Superbian science has.

rows.label: tlk44400287_03_msg0003
rows.name:
I fear whether we will really be able
to handle what comes next...

rows.label: tlk44400287_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I believe myself a rational man,
yet still, I find myself praying to
Adel for safety...
